  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/41d1fbd4918ea07f92ca3304ffb58679.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/41d1fbd4918ea07f92ca3304ffb58679.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it’s up to you alone to stop an alien invasion from the depths of the ocean in this legendary, home computer era shoot ‘em up dredged up and faithfully rebuilt for modern platforms – <strong>X-Out: Resurfaced!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=722 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/5e2e0ad48ab98691b61b637ed177c66f.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/5e2e0ad48ab98691b61b637ed177c66f.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 1990, the year of <strong>X-Out’s</strong> initial release on Amiga, it stood out as a breath of fresh seaside air in the stale shoot 'em-up space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partly, because it didn’t take part in “space” as so many games of its genre did (and still do) but instead went for a dive through underwater worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But what really pushed it further than its other side-scrolling competitors was its shop system allowing players to mix and match from a wide variety of ships, weapons, and other accessory parts to build their fleet making every playthrough (attempt) feel different and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now 2025 <strong>X-Out</strong> the highly challenging underwater shoot ‘em up from game developer legends <strong>Rainbow Arts</strong> is finally returning. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ININ</strong> and <strong>Ziggurat</strong> have collaborated to bring you a faithful remake completely rebuilt from the ground up and greatly improved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/2ccfdbfa62ac60c899ad23b01ef7cc53.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/2ccfdbfa62ac60c899ad23b01ef7cc53.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The impressive sprite work of yesteryear has not only been remade into even more impressive modern high-resolution sprites but also greatly expanded upon with particle and lighting effects. 8 varied stages, the enemies, the bosses, the ships, the projectiles; <strong>Everything shines in a brand-new light!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/113c9d885704531a22a2d2a7c7c7bcba.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/113c9d885704531a22a2d2a7c7c7bcba.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apart from the visual journey each playthrough, you’ll embark on a musical one as well: <strong>epic synth soundscapes</strong> that drive you forward by none other than yours truly, the magnificent <strong>Chris Huelsbeck</strong>. In addition to him remastering his original works, we have committed ourselves to creating 6 entirely new tracks as well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1142585ed6cc7e1cf870b984788ee267.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/1142585ed6cc7e1cf870b984788ee267.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not just Chris Hülsbeck, we also managed to get in contact with <strong>Ogan Kandemiroglu</strong>, brother and co-artist of <strong>Celal Kandemiroglu</strong> who created the original iconic key art of X-Out, to take on that task for the remake as a tribute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/8aaaacedce72c8b3e61fd454f868d220.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/8aaaacedce72c8b3e61fd454f868d220.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, the <strong>shop system is back and thoroughly improved</strong> as well: New preconfigured load-outs allow you to jump straight into the action, added item descriptions helping new cadets configure and build their fleet, and FINALLY marked the available slots for your weaponry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/4e26fcc35e7457ddd49f74d75a20e190.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/4e26fcc35e7457ddd49f74d75a20e190.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Should you still feel overwhelmed by X-Out’s challenge, then maybe it’s time for a co-captain. Enlist a friend and face the terrors from the ocean deep together in local <strong>2-player coop</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/594261434d9be8ddf4fae08375cd86ed.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/594261434d9be8ddf4fae08375cd86ed.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you think you’ve seen everything there is to the game already then prepare to have your bearing changed and your gyro twisted in the <strong>Mirror Mode</strong> and its reverse scrolling levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/5f6d6842b878018e29a2f724636e11d4.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/5f6d6842b878018e29a2f724636e11d4.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a fresh but faithful take on a <strong>real shoot-’em-up classic</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get dazzled by the new and <strong>beautiful sprite work</strong> mixed with shiny particle and lighting effects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a journey through new and old synth soundscapes courtesy of <strong>composer legend Chris Huelsbeck</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of three load-outs or build your own fleet in the <strong>improved shop system</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a trusty ally and face the depths together in a <strong>2-player couch coop</strong> dive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your world flipped, turned upside down in the <strong>Mirror Mode</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too challenging? Don't fret we got some cheats for you to breeze through the game with ease!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/41d1fbd4918ea07f92ca3304ffb58679.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/41d1fbd4918ea07f92ca3304ffb58679.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it’s up to you alone to stop an alien invasion from the depths of the ocean in this legendary, home computer era shoot ‘em up dredged up and faithfully rebuilt for modern platforms – <strong>X-Out: Resurfaced!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=722 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/c1c4dbf0b8669e9ae91a593bdcbf02ab.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/5e2e0ad48ab98691b61b637ed177c66f.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/5e2e0ad48ab98691b61b637ed177c66f.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 1990, the year of <strong>X-Out’s</strong> initial release on Amiga, it stood out as a breath of fresh seaside air in the stale shoot 'em-up space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partly, because it didn’t take part in “space” as so many games of its genre did (and still do) but instead went for a dive through underwater worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But what really pushed it further than its other side-scrolling competitors was its shop system allowing players to mix and match from a wide variety of ships, weapons, and other accessory parts to build their fleet making every playthrough (attempt) feel different and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now 2025 <strong>X-Out</strong> the highly challenging underwater shoot ‘em up from game developer legends <strong>Rainbow Arts</strong> is finally returning. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ININ</strong> and <strong>Ziggurat</strong> have collaborated to bring you a faithful remake completely rebuilt from the ground up and greatly improved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/3114e4a896a65193523a85cccf6a4583.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/2ccfdbfa62ac60c899ad23b01ef7cc53.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/2ccfdbfa62ac60c899ad23b01ef7cc53.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The impressive sprite work of yesteryear has not only been remade into even more impressive modern high-resolution sprites but also greatly expanded upon with particle and lighting effects. 8 varied stages, the enemies, the bosses, the ships, the projectiles; <strong>Everything shines in a brand-new light!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/113c9d885704531a22a2d2a7c7c7bcba.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/113c9d885704531a22a2d2a7c7c7bcba.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apart from the visual journey each playthrough, you’ll embark on a musical one as well: <strong>epic synth soundscapes</strong> that drive you forward by none other than yours truly, the magnificent <strong>Chris Huelsbeck</strong>. In addition to him remastering his original works, we have committed ourselves to creating 6 entirely new tracks as well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/b64c8e4bcd0f3f96841c9322bb4e8864.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1142585ed6cc7e1cf870b984788ee267.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/1142585ed6cc7e1cf870b984788ee267.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not just Chris Hülsbeck, we also managed to get in contact with <strong>Ogan Kandemiroglu</strong>, brother and co-artist of <strong>Celal Kandemiroglu</strong> who created the original iconic key art of X-Out, to take on that task for the remake as a tribute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/8aaaacedce72c8b3e61fd454f868d220.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/8aaaacedce72c8b3e61fd454f868d220.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, the <strong>shop system is back and thoroughly improved</strong> as well: New preconfigured load-outs allow you to jump straight into the action, added item descriptions helping new cadets configure and build their fleet, and FINALLY marked the available slots for your weaponry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/40f16466b786c0585ef69bf2e8472eae.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/4e26fcc35e7457ddd49f74d75a20e190.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/4e26fcc35e7457ddd49f74d75a20e190.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Should you still feel overwhelmed by X-Out’s challenge, then maybe it’s time for a co-captain. Enlist a friend and face the terrors from the ocean deep together in local <strong>2-player coop</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.poster.avif?t=1740034888\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.webm?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/1512f891bfba9dbee24d9642701958ba.mp4?t=1740034888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/594261434d9be8ddf4fae08375cd86ed.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/594261434d9be8ddf4fae08375cd86ed.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you think you’ve seen everything there is to the game already then prepare to have your bearing changed and your gyro twisted in the <strong>Mirror Mode</strong> and its reverse scrolling levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras/5f6d6842b878018e29a2f724636e11d4.avif?t=1740034888\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047070/extras_big/5f6d6842b878018e29a2f724636e11d4.avif?t=1740034888 width=800 height=67 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a fresh but faithful take on a <strong>real shoot-’em-up classic</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get dazzled by the new and <strong>beautiful sprite work</strong> mixed with shiny particle and lighting effects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a journey through new and old synth soundscapes courtesy of <strong>composer legend Chris Huelsbeck</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of three load-outs or build your own fleet in the <strong>improved shop system</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a trusty ally and face the depths together in a <strong>2-player couch coop</strong> dive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your world flipped, turned upside down in the <strong>Mirror Mode</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too challenging? Don't fret we got some cheats for you to breeze through the game with ease!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
